      "content": "counselors and support groups won't pay back the millions i owe or take away the sense that i've failed everyone who ever believed in me. it feels like there's no path back to being \"me\" again. i just want the noise to stop. i just want a way out of this crushing feeling, a permanent way to just... not have to deal with this anymore. it feels like the only way to actually protect them from my failure is to just not be a burden on them anymore.",
